## ğŸ‘‹ Overview

This repository contains a **production-grade end-to-end automation test framework** built using **Playwright with TypeScript**, designed to validate critical user journeys on the Advantage Online Shopping demo eâ€‘commerce application:

ğŸ”— **Application Under Test (AUT):** [https://www.advantageonlineshopping.com/](https://www.advantageonlineshopping.com/)

The framework is architected following **top 1% automation engineering standards**, emphasizing:

* Clean **Page Object Model (POM)** design
* Reliable and deterministic test execution
* Realistic user behavior simulation
* Maintainability, scalability, and CI/CD readiness

---

## ğŸ¯ Test Objectives Covered

The automated suite validates the following core customer journeys:

1. **User Management**

   * Create a new user account
   * Login with valid credentials
   * Logout successfully
   * Validate error handling for invalid login attempts

2. **Eâ€‘Commerce Purchase Flow**

   * Add a product to the cart
   * Start checkout as a loggedâ€‘out user (redirect to login)
   * Complete checkout as a loggedâ€‘in user
   * Complete direct payment flow using SafePay

