### ğŸ”‘ Design Principles Applied

* **Strict POM separation** (No assertions inside tests leaking into page layers)
* **Single responsibility** per page class
* **Resilient locators** (role-based & attribute-based selectors)
* **Explicit assertions** for navigation, visibility, and state validation
* **Chromium-first execution** as per requirement

