## ğŸ” Test Data Strategy

* **Static test credentials** are used for demo stability
* User creation uses deterministic data (can be enhanced with UUID/randomization if required)
* Payment flow uses **SafePay sandbox credentials** only

> âš ï¸ Since this is a public demo site, occasional instability is expected. Timeouts and assertions are tuned accordingly.

