## ğŸ§  Engineering Best Practices Followed

âœ” Page Object Model (POM)
âœ” Explicit waits with meaningful assertions
âœ” Zero hard sleeps (`waitForTimeout` avoided)
âœ” Readable, businessâ€‘aligned test names
âœ” CI/CD friendly (Azure DevOps / GitHub Actions ready)
âœ” Scalable structure for future test expansion

